1. 徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n 2. 釋放所有因反送中被捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n 3. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n 4.追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n 5. 立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>七區集會</ins></span></strong></span><br />\n  日期：8月5日<br />\n  時間：下午一時開始<br />\n各區地點：金鐘添馬公園、旺角麥花臣球場、沙田百步梯、大埔廣福球場、荃灣沙咀道球場、黃大仙廣場、屯門公園<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ttLCv36.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FttLCv36.jpg&h=09ba4839&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NKejKpu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNKejKpu.jpg&h=f51b4d73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[行動全面升級] 7.30。8.5全港罷工。全民抗爭。遍地開花七區集會 [人手置頂]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1380326/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1380326/page/1</a></div>"},{"pid":"35d5cb330663e7e970f1d322fd9ddf2a9fd30515","tid":1381294,"uid":65887,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:05:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/4d0/a18/4d0a1882f6121a55d26d98c992522a3e1d3eec43_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2F4d0%2Fa18%2F4d0a1882f6121a55d26d98c992522a3e1d3eec43_n.jpg&h=46809919&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c60ded1fcd2f2cd4d27f8fbd98f01cb76aee79f2","tid":1381294,"uid":68463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:06:58.000Z","msg":"咁都得 姐係以後個個差佬都揸呢支野扑頭啦?"},{"pid":"a027ca6e20c6618d7fe892ca60ae11df69091d51","tid":1381294,"uid":132770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:07:31.000Z","msg":"即係叫人升級到你棍都冇機會掹啦"},{"pid":"fc05e21d84340b28eb95af77afc570e1505f916a","tid":1381294,"uid":33147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:08:17.000Z","msg":"即使係索帶都有尖頭位 可以打爆頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"318e70fee9308809a71c4ab680296902820